@alexandrelimassantana I agree with you about the code changes.
However, this commit only reverts the commit 9c4162a and 16baa12 to fix the issue.

The issue you mentioned does exist in our codebase,  not only in these two commands, but more than 10 other commands (some are implemented in different way), you can change them in a single PR if you want.

